sonarr_episodefile_episodeoverviews: Sumomo informs Shinbo of an excessive amount of data collected and asks what could be deleted. While offering different choices, Shinbo reminisces of the experiences of said deletable data. Shinbo then decides to keep everything and just buy Sumomo more memory.|Minoru and Yuzuki recap over what has happened so far regarding Chi and Hideki.|Hibiya and Kotoko retell the final third of the series between Hideki and Chi.|A six-minute feature focusing on an adventure with Sumomo and Kotoko where they chase down Chi. This was shown at some anime conventions and can also be found on the Chat Room DVD.
